{"color":"RED","isTrashed":false,"isPinned":false,"isArchived":false,"annotations":[{"description":"A conversational AI system that listens, learns, and challenges","source":"WEBLINK","title":"ChatGPT","url":"https://chatgpt.com/gpts/editor/g-52aO17yQq"}],"textContent":"// ==============================\n//  EAZY's DUAL SNEAK CONFIG\n//  FULL SYNC: CROSSHAIR + HUD + SOUND + RADARZOOM\n//  SHIFT + CTRL kombinierter Sneak-State\n// ==============================\n\n// --- SOUND SETTINGS ---\nalias stdv \"volume 0.33\"\nalias 1voicevol \"volume 0.22;voice_scale 0.3\"    // Leiser Modus (Sneak)\nalias 0voicevol \"stdv;voice_scale 0.5\"           // Normaler Modus\nstdv\n\n// --- CROSSHAIR SETTINGS ---\n// Standard: hellgrün (Custom RGB)\nalias mycross \"cl_crosshaircolor 5;cl_crosshaircolor_r 155;cl_crosshaircolor_g 255;cl_crosshaircolor_b 0\" // Hellgrün\n// Sneaken: Weiß\nalias sneakkross \"cl_crosshaircolor 5;cl_crosshaircolor_r 255;cl_crosshaircolor_g 255;cl_crosshaircolor_b 255\" // Weiß\n\n// --- HUD COLOR SETTINGS ---\nalias myhud \"cl_hud_color 4\"       // Teamfarben (Standardzustand)\nalias sneakhud \"cl_hud_color 8\"    // Weiß im Sneakmodus\n\n// --- RADARZOOM SETTINGS ---\nalias radarzoom_on \"cl_radar_scale 0.3;cl_radar_always_centered 0;cl_radar_rotate 0;cl_hud_radar_scale 1.113\"\nalias radarzoom_off \"cl_radar_scale 0.65;cl_radar_always_centered 1;cl_radar_rotate 1;cl_hud_radar_scale 1.337\"\n\nalias +radarzoom \"cl_autohelp true;1voicevol;radarzoom_on\"   // Radar Zoom an\nalias -radarzoom \"cl_autohelp false;0voicevol;radarzoom_off\" // Radar Zoom aus\n\n// --- VISUAL + AUDIO + RADAR COMBO ---\nalias <vol \"sneakkross;sneakhud;1voicevol;+radarzoom\"        // Sneaken: Weißes Crosshair/HUD + Leiser + Radarzoom an\nalias vol> \"mycross;myhud;0voicevol;-radarzoom\"              // Normal: Grün + Team-HUD + Normaler Sound + Radarzoom aus\n\n// --- STATE MACHINE (Mehrfachtasten-Handling) ---\nalias sne_on sne_enter1\nalias sne_off noop\nalias noop \"\"\n\nalias sne_enter1 \"<vol; alias sne_on noop; alias sne_off sne_maybe_exit1\"\nalias sne_maybe_exit1 \"alias sne_off sne_exit; alias sne_on sne_enter2\"\nalias sne_enter2 \"alias sne_off sne_maybe_exit1; alias sne_on noop\"\nalias sne_exit \"vol>; alias sne_on sne_enter1; alias sne_off noop\"\n\n// --- SNEAK (CTRL) ---\nalias +sneak_ctrl \"+duck; sne_on\"\nalias -sneak_ctrl \"sne_off; -duck\"\n\n// --- WALK/SCHLEICHEN (SHIFT) ---\n// Für klassisches langsames Gehen statt Sprint: ersetze +sprint/-sprint mit +speed/-speed\nalias +sneak_shift \"+sprint; sne_on\"\nalias -sneak_shift \"sne_off; -sprint\"\n\n// --- KEY BINDS ---\nbind ctrl +sneak_ctrl\nbind shift +sneak_shift\n\n// ==============================\n//  WIRKUNG:\n//  - SHIFT oder CTRL drücken → Sneak aktiv\n//      Crosshair = Weiß\n//      HUD = Weiß\n//      Sound = Leiser\n//      Radar = Vergrößert (mit fixierter Karte)\n//  - Erst wenn beide losgelassen → Normalzustand\n//      Crosshair = Hellgrün (155,255,0)\n//      HUD = Teamfarben\n//      Sound = Normal\n//      Radar = Normalzoom (zentriert & rotierend)\n// ==============================\n\n","title":"","userEditedTimestampUsec":1762708165452000,"createdTimestampUsec":1762707142469000,"textContentHtml":"<p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">// ==============================<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-height:1.38;margin-top:0.0pt;margin-bottom:0.0pt;\"><span style=\"font-size:7.2pt;font-family:'Google Sans';color:#000000;background-color:transparent;font-weight:400;font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre;white-space:pre-wrap;\">//&nbsp; EAZY's DUAL SNEAK CONFIG<\/span><\/p><p dir=\"ltr\" style=\"line-hei